    <arm_group_type>Experimental</arm_group_type>
    <description>Twenty-fourth consecutive patients with histologically proved pancreatic cancer [stage IIb (n=4), III (n=15), IV (n=5) ]underwent intraoperative RFA of primary tumor.</description>
